check.output-format:
Emit to stdout:

```
SUCCESS
Register: {absolute path to the persisted risk register}
Approach: {what was assessed}
Categories scanned: {the risk lenses applied}
Risks: {N} ({count} High/High, {count} High-impact, {count} other)
Top risks:
  - {risk} — likelihood/impact — mitigated by {standard mitigation} [cite]
  - {risk} — likelihood/impact — mitigated by {standard mitigation} [cite]
Assessed internal-only: {categories without web research, or "none"}
```

Present to the user:

## Risk Reconnaissance Complete

**Register**: {path}
**Approach**: {what was assessed}
**Categories scanned**: {lenses}

**Top risks** (by likelihood × impact):
- {risk} — {likelihood}/{impact} — mitigated by {mitigation} [cite]
- {risk} — {likelihood}/{impact} — mitigated by {mitigation} [cite]

{note any category assessed from internal evidence only}

Then offer next actions:
- Deepen a top risk (Focused Study)
- Compare mitigation approaches (Comparative Matrix)
